            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Take your<strong> chicken</strong> out of the fridge and open the packet to let it breathe before cooking</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Heat a separate, large, wide-based pan (preferably nonstick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Chop the <strong>cherry</strong> <strong>tomatoes</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1638875489718-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
