            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>When the pan with the vegetable oil is hot, add the<strong> diced chicken thigh</strong> with the <strong>sun-dried</strong> <strong>tomato paste</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until beginning to brown</p><p>Once the other pan is hot, add the <strong>gnocchi</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1638875494164-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1638875494164-x400.jpg",
