            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1638875494164-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cook the gnocchi for 4-5 min or until golden and starting to crisp</p><p>Tip: Give the gnocchi a shake in the pan once in a while to make sure they are crisping all over!</p><p>Wash the <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with<strong> kitchen paper</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1638875497955-x200.jpg",
