            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1638875497955-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has started to brown, remove the pan from the heat, then add the <strong>spinach</strong> and <strong>halved</strong> <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Return the pan to the heat, then cook for 2-3 min or until the spinach has wilted and chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Note: Please make sure you cook your chicken thoroughly (until piping hot!) as cooking equipment varies</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1638875502195-x200.jpg",
