            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked, add the <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>and <strong>garlic & herb spread </strong>to the pan with 50ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [100ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>creamy tomato & chicken sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
