        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once golden and crisp, add the <strong>gnocchi</strong> to the<strong> creamy tomato & chicken sauce</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>creamy tomato & chicken gnocchi</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p>",
